    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/5fb2e598a3ccb475128e2fea48f52b27.avif?t=1762420869\" width=754 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/87a346a29be5f269a3e3bdef1a11883f.avif?t=1762420869\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras_big/87a346a29be5f269a3e3bdef1a11883f.avif?t=1762420869 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong> </strong> <br> <br><br>你将扮演农场管理者，完成时间科技有限公司下达的KPI指标。      <br>你将通过紧张刺激的抽卡！     <br>规避或利用时间爆炸💥！     <br>获得卡包和宝箱，     <br>构建你的卡组，     <br>打出卡牌获得金币收益！     <br>你还需要有策略性地选择前进的路线，游戏中你会遇到丰富的抉择事件、灾年和大天灾挑战。 <br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/fe9e904a87909860368afc62e43d3788.avif?t=1762420869\" width=754 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a748ff21d94eb1ad625466fb54b447d7.poster.avif?t=1762420869\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a748ff21d94eb1ad625466fb54b447d7.webm?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a748ff21d94eb1ad625466fb54b447d7.mp4?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong> <br><br><br> 你将拥有一个神奇的袋子，袋子里装满了无数张各具特色的卡牌 每张牌都有其【时间值】  <br>每回合中，你需要在有限的【时间值上限】中  <br>从袋子里尽量抽出【更多】的牌！  <br>😮要不要再抽一张？  <br>😏再抽一张？  <br>😫再抽一张？  <br> 你说了算！  <br> 你的每一次选择，都可能是神来之笔……或是噩梦的开端！   <br>但请注意，如果超出了时间值上限，将会产生时间爆炸💥!  <br>时间爆炸也不全是坏事，在游戏中如果你能拿到合适的牌，可以很好地利用或者规避哦👌 <br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/17ee4e85d5a0476cb2496a45d8a76530.avif?t=1762420869\" width=754 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/85a291598661e2c5be81da3ec0d08dbe.poster.avif?t=1762420869\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/85a291598661e2c5be81da3ec0d08dbe.webm?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/85a291598661e2c5be81da3ec0d08dbe.mp4?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我们已经设计了：<br>300+张独特卡牌：法术，植物，动物，建筑，衍生物；  <br>200+个强力挂件：与各种流派或者卡牌达成combo！或者加强你的游戏体验！  <br>浅浅地统计，游戏至少能够拥有数十种不同的流派可供选择，个中体验尽不相同！  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/b152a62e30a4955542503e2fbc67d9fd.avif?t=1762420869\" width=754 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/9a2e49bfdaf5b21212f0557316f300ad.avif?t=1762420869\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras_big/9a2e49bfdaf5b21212f0557316f300ad.avif?t=1762420869 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>以时间为主轴，在游戏前进的道路上你将会遇到：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+个富有抉择性的地图事件；   <br>20+种棘手但奖励丰富的灾年；   <br>10+种机制特殊的大天灾； <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/01f4aaca374c5fd641024ec87acaa662.avif?t=1762420869\" width=754 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a6385f1ac6c7d6f3c12bf7e9e93fd68c.poster.avif?t=1762420869\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a6385f1ac6c7d6f3c12bf7e9e93fd68c.webm?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177890/extras/a6385f1ac6c7d6f3c12bf7e9e93fd68c.mp4?t=1762420869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong> <br> <br> <br>在游戏中你将可以： <br>开各种卡包！ <br>开各种补给箱！  <br>还有呱呱乐！  <br>获得金币、卡牌、挂件 游戏提供了各种不同的奖励获取渠道！ <br>为游戏打造了更多丰富的体验和进阶渠道！</p>",
